 county with a low rate of active cases. Out-of-state guests are strongly encouraged to [sign up with Sara Alert](https://apps.health.vermont.gov/EpiInfoWebSurvey/Home/9c2e5941-1ba7-4ab4-84be-558ba7684f5d) – a free, automated and secure reminder system to check for [common symptoms of COVID-19](https://www.healthvermont.gov/response/coronavirus-covid-19/about-coronavirus-disease-covid-19) – for daily reminders from the Vermont Department of Health.\n\nIf you have a concern about lodging facilities that are violating the Be Smart, Stay Safe Order, fill out the Department of Public Safety's online [non-compliance complaint form](http://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=O5O0IK26PEOcAnDtzHVZxp8VoIcMV9NNu0QyG_vdGAVUN1pLSTdOMERRR1dXOVpZMDBZUEtNVlhXMi4u).",
