ently under quarantine who has had no symptoms during the first seven days of quarantine. Find more details under [“I am under a 14-day quarantine. Can I have the option to be tested and end my quarantine period?”](https://apps.health.vermont.gov/COVID/faq/#4692) on this page. ",
