                "question": "Where can I get tested for COVID-19?",
                "answerBody": "**Not everyone needs to be tested for COVID-19.** Use [CDC’s Self-Checker](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/testing/index.html) to find out if you should be tested. If you think you may need to get tested, talk with your health care provider, or call 2-1-1 if you don’t have a provider and need to be connected to care.\n\nIf you:\n\n*   have [**symptoms of COVID-19**](https://www.healthvermont.gov/response/coronavirus-covid-19/about-coronavirus-disease-covid-19#prevention) **–** contact your health care provider to ask about a test\n*   are in **quarantine because of travel** – contact your health care provider to ask about a test on or after day 7 of quarantine\n*   are in **quarantine because you are a** [**close contact of someone with COVID-19**](https://www.healthvermont.gov/sites/default/files/documents/pdf/COVID-19_What-to-do-if-you-are-a-close-contact-of-someone-with-COVID-19_final.pdf)– contact your health care provider to ask about a test on or after day 7 of quarantine\n*   need a test to **prepare for a medical procedure** – arrange a test through the health care provider who is doing your procedure\n*   have **no symptoms and are not in quarantine** – use [CDC’s Self-Checker](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/testing/index.html) to find out if you should be tested. If you do need testing, look for a clinic or pharmacy that offers testing near you, or [register at a pop-up location](https://www.healthvermont.gov/response/coronavirus-covid-19/testing-covid-19#popup).\n\nFind more information about [testing and testing locations](https://www.healthvermont.gov/response/coronavirus-covid-19/testing-covid-19) including frequently asked [questions about pop-up testing](https://www.healthvermont.gov/response/coronavirus-covid-19/testing-covid-19).\n\nFind out [what to do if you are sick](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/if-you-are-sick/index.html) from the CDC and what to do while you’re [waiting for test 