    {
        "id": 4736,
        "revisions": [
            {
                "question": "I traveled internationally or by cruise ship. Do I or my household members need to quarantine?",
                "answerBody": "If you’ve returned from international travel or from a cruise ship or river cruise voyage, follow the CDC’s [after travel guidance](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/after-travel-precautions.html) when you return to the U.S. When you return to Vermont, you must quarantine for 14 days. You have the option to get a PCR test on day 7 of your quarantine. Find out how under “[I am under a 14-day quarantine. Can I have the option to be tested and end my quarantine period?](https://apps.health.vermont.gov/COVID/faq/#4692)” on this page.\n\nOther members of your household who did not travel do not need to quarantine, but should observe themselves for symptoms for 14 days.\n\nLearn about [isolation, quarantine and self-observation](https://www.healthvermont.gov/sites/default/files/documents/pdf/COVID-19-chart-observation-isolation-quarantine_final.pdf).\n\nIf you or your household members develop [symptoms of COVID-19](https://www.healthvermont.gov/response/coronavirus-covid-19/about-coronavirus-disease-covid-19), contact your health care provider right away. If you do not have a health care provider, call 2-1-1 to be connected to care, or contact the nearest [federally qualified health center](https://bistatepca.org/community-resources/vt-health-centers) or one of [Vermont’s free & referral clinics](https://vtfreeclinics.org/).\n\nFind more information from the CDC about: \n\n* [returning from cruise ship and river cruise voyages](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/returning-cruise-voyages.html)\n* [travel recommendations by country](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/map-and-travel-notices.html) \n* [FAQs for Travelers](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/faqs.html)",
                "date": "2020-08-31"
            }
        ],
        "deletedDate": "2020-09-03"
    },
