ps://www.healthvermont.gov/sites/default/files/documents/pdf/COVID19-Schools-Holiday-Travel-Toolkit.pdf) to help you consider your plans carefully and communicate with others about the risks. The toolkit includes travel questions families can ask themselves, information on how to acknowledge the challenges of the difficult decisions about whether and how to travel, and considering alternatives to travel or hosting guests.\n\nCelebrating holidays within your own household or sharing a meal virtually will not be the same as we’re used to, but we need to keep our guard up and continue to do all we can to keep from getting or spreading COVID-19.\n\nRead the CDC’s [tips for celebrating Thanksgiving](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/daily-life-coping/holidays/thanksgiving.html).",
